      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING VIOLET (1) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (29.70) at this track over 520m. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can find winning form. RITZA KRIS (3) scored by 2.75 lengths last time (29.41) in a Grade 4/5 over 515m at The Gardens. Has already won two times from this draw. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. RED ROCK RAZZLE (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (29.78) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. In the mix. OVERFLOW JENNY (4) comes off a (29.69) win last time, scoring by a nose in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Has already won two times from this draw.",
